BUSINESS REQUIREMENT DOCUMENT (BRD)
Project: Sales Performance Analysis and Solution System

1. Introduction  
The purpose of this document is to define the business requirements for the Sales Performance Analysis System. This system helps businesses analyze sales data, identify problems, and recommend solutions.

2. Business Objective  
- Improve sales performance through data-driven decisions  
- Identify low performing regions and products  
- Increase revenue and reduce losses  
- Provide management with actionable insights  

3. Stakeholders  
- Business Owner  
- Sales Manager  
- Data Analyst  
- Business Analyst  
- IT Team  
- End Users  

4. Business Problems  
- No centralized sales analysis  
- Manual reporting causes delays  
- Hard to identify low-performing regions  
- Poor decision making due to lack of insights  

5. Business Requirements  
- System should accept sales data  
- System should analyze revenue and units sold  
- Identify low-performing areas  
- Provide visual dashboards  
- Generate business solutions  

6. Scope  
In Scope:
- Data Analysis
- Dashboard creation
- Business insights
- Reports

Out of Scope:
- Payment systems
- ERP integration
- CRM automation

7. Business Value  
- Faster decision making  
- Increased revenue  
- Reduced losses  
- Improved operational efficiency
